Package: stablemarriage
Type: Package
Title: Fundamental algorithm for the stable marriage problem
Version: 1.0
Date: 2022-03-08
Author: Danielle Notice
Maintainer: Danielle Notice <d.a.notice@lancaster.ac.uk>
Description: A package which implements the fundamental algorithm of the stable marriage algorithm as described by 
  Donald E. Knuth and Martin Goldstein in "Stable Marriage and Its Relation to Other Combinatorial Problems : An Introduction to the Mathematical Analysis of Algorithms".
  The package also includes useful functions for creating and checking preference tables, as well as example data.
  Built in R version 3.6.3.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.8)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
